episodes.title: Zachary Quinto, ﻿Shailene Woodley, ﻿Barbie Ferreira Discuss Cult of Love on Broadway
episodes.description: Leslye Headland's Cult of Love officially opened on Broadway at Second Stage's Helen Hayes Theater December 12. Centering on the four adult children of the Dahl family and their partners as they return home for a rocky holiday gathering, the play marks Headland's Broadway debut. Headland was the show-runner on Star Wars: Acolyte.
